title: International Nature Loving Association
description: INLA, founded in 2010, is part of the worldwide INLA organizations in several continents and its mission is to bring everyone, especially the young and future generations, to respect lives, to love nature, to be compassionate towards the earth and its living beings. INLA sends its message through nature songs and dances and social & environmental awareness activities (e.g. tree planting, school visits, etc).
